title: HELP ME OUT HOMES
body: I've had a few chat restrictions this season but haven't had one in 3 months or so and i still cannot earn chest or key rewards, i just read that people with chat restrictions can't earn ending season rewards either. Can i still earn that ending season reward or am i Fkd?

replies.body:
2016 Ranked rewards haven't been announced yet. I'd recommend keeping an eye on the [News page](http://euw.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/) for the official announcement when it comes out.

Let me know if you have any other questions.
